
bz-owl release notes
====================

1.4 (2014-04-02)
--
* /web/index.php now calls a new add-on called pathLoaderSystem
* pathLoaderSystem add-on uses modules that can flag a user as banned
* improved loginSystem logic and its local login module now logs invalid attempts (5 invalid attempts within 1 day disable login ability for 1 day, beginning with oldest invalid attempt during the day)
* local login module of loginSystem can now set special permissions
* logout now works with new logoutSystem add-on
* match rss now built by matchServicesRSSSystem
* renamed players* classes to users*
* updated smarty engine
* team page is now handled by new teamSystem add-on
* classes have been enhanced to follow the MVC scheme

1.3.2 (2011-07-25)
--
* loginSystem add-on sets user join date properly now

1.3.1 (2011-07-23)
--
* fixed account activation query
* pageSystem add-on can now add new pages

1.3 (2011-07-22)
--
* Replaced login add-on with a entirely new loginSystem that provides a better framework
* fixed a bug that did not reset a user's teamid upon deletion of a team
* New pageSystem add-on to control which page is shown without directly editing db

1.2.1 (2011-06-23)
--
* Minor theme changes
* show unfinished themes by config option
* updated db structure to avoid periods in table names
* Partial reimplementation of Teams page by a new teamSystem add-on

1.2 (2011-05-13)
---
* overall code re-organisation, concentrating on readability
* several database structure changes to fit new add-on system
* rename player to user at new code
* new login add-on (in progress)
* new maintenance add-on (partially done)
* fix some markup problems
* serve xhtml using MIME type application/xhtml+xml on production environment
* implement database update script
* db class error reporting with fallback to text file
* add example teamStats add-on
* downgrade web/CMS/announcements to keep compatibility with ducati code
* implement new pm system as add-on
* implement new static page editor as add-on
* implement new news system as add-on
* drop Login, News, Rules, FAQ, Links, Contact and Bans folders
* add 6x7 prototype theme (partially done)
* add example .htaccess file to use with new add-on loader
* implement add-on loader script, using new lookup table in db
* switch to smarty template engine
* rename web/styles to web/themes

1.1 (2011-02-25)
--
* display of private messages using new code, otherwise use old code
* drop web/CMS/navi.inc and replace it by the new Layout.php and the templates
* add php.template in styles dir and per theme for old world pages
* new code does no longer use web/CMS/siteinfo.hp
* add web/CMS/classes to be used by new web/CMS/site.php
* new site config settings using settings.php
* new code uses integrated template library
* new code uses PDO

1.0 (2010-10-06)
--
* initial stable release



